{"tid":1590003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"10.1 示威時勿忘叫口號","createTime":"2019-09-23T13:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T14:16:24.000Z","uid":161701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2cd46ab54c5bbb963159327b8f62dfe771286c59","tid":1590003,"uid":161701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:50:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">十月一日 全城開花 </span><br />\n                    <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勿戀戰港島</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家示威時勿忘叫口號</span></span><br />\n                <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一、全面撤回逃犯條例修訂草案（暫時成功）<br />\n二、根據香港法例第86章成立有法律約束力的獨立調查委員會（特別係第二，成立獨立委員會！）<br />\n三、收回六一二暴動定性<br />\n四、撤銷對「反送中」抗爭者的無理控罪<br />\n五、落實真普選</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10.1日 香港人 加油！"},{"pid":"25a2f69d536a94fbc29a53aa7ea00e2207449907","tid":1590003,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"d3f7b1594dbd8bb12a669d53a05e0ec4cd4e2893","tid":1590003,"uid":63482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:16:24.000Z","msg":"仲有一齊唱願榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}